  "abstract": "Alectra vogelii Benth. (Scrophulariacee) is a root parasite of peanut and several other leguminous crop olants.  It has been reported in various countries in Africa (Angola, Burkina Faso, Malawi, Mozambique, Nigeria, Swaziland, Zambia, and Zimbabwe)...",
